One day jake went on a walk outside
Jake called his friends and asked if they wanted to join
Jakes friends said "yes" and he was very excited
After jakes friends came and joined him,It started raining so jake was sad
Next,Jake and his friends went to jakes house and they were all sad because they wanted to walk outside
They were all sitting in jakes room and they were bored
After that,they started to play hide and seek at jakes house
They all realized how much fun they can have inside of their house as well as outside 